            "documentation": "HOW TO USE:\nPick the honey tree you want to get an encounter from, then pick the corresponding offset. Slather honey on the tree, then execute this ACE using that tree's offset. The pokemon will be ready to encounter immediately. Each time you use a honey at that tree, the pokemon spawned will re-roll. If you do not slather honey on the tree and use this ACE, you will encounter the previous pokemon encountered there. (Sometimes the honey tree will not visually shake, but the encounters should be there regardless)\n\nHONEY TREE OFFSETS:\n\nSouthern Route 205 - Offset: 0x74F8\n\nNorthern Route 205 - Offset: 0x7500\n\nRoute 206  - Offset: 0x7508\n\nRoute 207  - Offset: 0x7510\n\nRoute 208  - Offset: 0x7518\n\nRoute 209  - Offset: 0x7520\n\nSouthern Route 210  - Offset: 0x7528\n\nNorthern Route 210  - Offset: 0x7530\n\nEastern Route 211  - Offset: 0x7538\n\nNorthern Route 212  - Offset: 0x7540\n\nSouthern Route 212  - Offset: 0x7548\n\nRoute 213  - Offset: 0x7550\n\nRoute 214 - Offset: 0x7558\n\nRoute 215 - Offset: 0x7560\n\nRoute 218 - Offset: 0x7568\n\nRoute 221 - Offset: 0x7570\n\nRoute 222 - Offset: 0x7578\n\nValley Windworks - Offset: 0x7580\n\nEterna Forest exterior - Offset: 0x7588\n\nFuego Ironworks - Offset: 0x7590\n\nFloaroma Meadow - Offset: 0x7598\n\n\nHOW IT WORKS: Each honey tree has a value assigned to it, 0-1440. When the player slathers on honey to a honey tree, it sets the value to 1440. Each minute the value will count down by 1. (There is a minor timer bug, more info here on how the game actually counts down the honey tree value... https://sinjohruins.com/timerbug.html)a\n\nWhen the value of a honey tree is 0, there will be no honey on the tree, and the player may slather some on it\nAt 1440-1081, there will be honey on the tree, and the player may slather some one it (setting the value back to 1440)\nAt 1080-1, you will be able to encounter the pokemon at the honey tree. \n\n1080 corresponds to 6 hours passing. 24 hours = 1440, 6 hours = 360. 1440-360=1080. The encounter will remain at the tree until that tree's timer reaches 0, or roughly 18 hours. I access the address of the honey tree, and write its value to 1080, making the encounter instantly available."
